Description: This package allows to preform the entire pipeline of calculations for Hg isotopic dilution.    The first step rsd_MMHg_ratios and rsd_IHg_ratios allow us to check the variance between injections. First the ratio between the isotpes is calculated, secondly we calculate the mean, sd and rsd of each ratio and corroborate that the rsd stays within the cut-off.
